84
00:05:48,566 --> 00:05:50,033
You know, I'm really
lucky to have Chi

85
00:05:50,100 --> 00:05:52,900
to help out around here;
she's a very good worker.

86
00:05:52,966 --> 00:05:54,900
Then, I guess everything's fine.

87
00:05:54,966 --> 00:05:56,700
But listen.

88
00:05:56,766 --> 00:05:58,566
If there is ever anything
you need help with,

89
00:05:58,633 --> 00:06:00,133
