to find me, right?

90
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:01,500
Motosuwa.

91
00:06:01,566 --> 00:06:04,433
I was a total wreck
after Chi disappeared,

92
00:06:04,500 --> 00:06:06,166
and you were there for me.

93
00:06:06,233 --> 00:06:08,433
