after talking to you.

94
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:09,800
So, I'd like to do the same

95
00:06:09,866 --> 00:06:11,366
if you need someone to talk to.

96
00:06:11,433 --> 00:06:12,533
But don't take it the wrong way!

97
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:14,866
