you back, of course.

98
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,900
I really appreciate it.

99
00:06:18,966 --> 00:06:21,900
But I'm serious: there's nothing
the matter with me at all.

100
00:06:21,966 --> 00:06:24,300
I just tend to be a
little awkward sometimes.

101
00:06:24,366 --> 00:06:25,633
Huh?

102
00:06:27,433 --> 00:06:29,166
