myself to get rid of it.

116
00:07:04,833 --> 00:07:06,566
Huh?

117
00:07:07,466 --> 00:07:09,400
Did Chi make a mistake?

118
00:07:09,466 --> 00:07:11,166
Oh no, I'm the one
who made the mistake;

119
00:07:11,233 --> 00:07:12,600
I should never have left it out.

120
00:07:12,666 --> 00:07:14,033
I'm sorry about that, Chi.

121
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,633
Why don't you come with me, Chi,

122
00:07:31,700 --> 00:07:33,466
I've got your uniform over here.

123
00:07:34,100 --> 00:07:35,033
Yumi!

124
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:36,533
Huh?

125
00:07:41,233 --> 00:07:44,100
