Chi for me, please?!

126
00:07:45,233 --> 00:07:47,100
Motosuwa, you shouldn't...

127
00:07:55,866 --> 00:07:57,033
Yumi!

128
00:08:02,533 --> 00:08:03,600
Yumi!

129
00:08:09,700 --> 00:08:10,733
There's one thing I'm good at,

130
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:12,733
