132
00:08:15,866 --> 00:08:18,266
So are Persocoms really
the best after all?

133
00:08:18,333 --> 00:08:20,300
They're better than
real women, aren't they?!

134
00:08:20,366 --> 00:08:22,466
Better than any woman, anywhere!

135
00:08:23,900 --> 00:08:28,100
He told me he made
that outfit just for me.

136
00:08:28,166 --> 00:08:30,700
But n-now a Persocom's...

137
00:08:30,766 --> 00:08:31,400
Huh?

138
00:08:31,466 --> 00:08:32,500
So does this mean the new dress

139
00:08:32,566 --> 00:08:35,766
that Chi put on was actually
meant for you to wear?

140
00:08:42,433 --> 00:08:43,433
Does it hurt?

141
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:44,700
Huh?

142
00:08:44,766 --> 00:08:47,433
Do you hurt right here?
Is it an injury?

143
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:49,500
I'm not injured, Chi,
but thanks a lot.

144
00:08:49,566 --> 00:08:51,166
But Chi doesn't understand.

145
00:08:51,233 --> 00:08:53,400
Manager had a painful face.

146
00:08:53,466 --> 00:08:55,033
It's still there.

147
00:08:57,533 --> 00:08:59,433
Why does it always come to this?

148
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:01,900
I just made her cry again.

149
00:09:01,966 --> 00:09:03,633
Not only that, I hesitated

150
00:09:03,700 --> 00:09:05,566
when I should
have gone after her.

151
00:09:05,633 --> 00:09:07,533
But Manager, it's different.

152
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,900
Yumi cried because
of Chi this time.

153
00:09:09,966 --> 00:09:11,433
When she looked at Chi.

154
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:13,733
