seem to get over her.

159
00:09:38,533 --> 00:09:40,566
Telephone!

160
00:09:40,633 --> 00:09:43,833
Telephone! Telephone!

161
00:09:45,300 --> 00:09:46,233
No answer.

162
00:09:46,300 --> 00:09:49,133
Switching from telephone
to voice mail mode now!

163
