165
00:09:57,033 --> 00:09:59,066
May I help you?

166
00:09:59,133 --> 00:10:00,266
Where's my applause?

167
00:10:00,333 --> 00:10:01,233
Huh?

168
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:02,266
An ovation!

169
00:10:02,333 --> 00:10:04,066
Sumomo has just done a fine job!

170
00:10:04,133 --> 00:10:05,433
There should be applause!

171
00:10:05,500 --> 00:10:07,233
Why do I even bother?

172
00:10:08,100 --> 00:10:10,300
So what about my applause?

173
00:10:11,766 --> 00:10:13,633
Yay! Woohoo!

174
00:10:13,700 --> 00:10:14,433
Sumomo got applause!
I got applause!

175
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:16,033
What is it with
this place anyway?

176
00:10:16,100 --> 00:10:19,100
All the Persocoms around here
are so strange, including Chi.

177
00:10:20,900 --> 00:10:22,533
Hey! They're back!

178
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:24,933
Welcome back!

179
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,500
Is this person a guest of yours?

180
00:10:34,566 --> 00:10:37,333
Yeah. So can you guys
keep it down for a while?

181
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:38,833
Aye!

182
00:10:44,900 --> 00:10:47,966
