to marry a Persocom?

257
00:14:02,333 --> 00:14:04,766
Oh, well I had some
reservations, or course.

258
00:14:04,833 --> 00:14:06,800
For one thing, I was concerned
whether her marrying me

259
00:14:06,866 --> 00:14:08,600
would really make
her happy or not.

260
00:14:08,666 --> 00:14:10,966
But then, there all kinds
of different marriages

261
00:14:11,033 --> 00:14:12,533
out there in the world,
and even though this one

262
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:14,533
may seem a little
unusual to some people,

263
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:15,866
I thought we'd be
able to build on

264
00:14:15,933 --> 00:14:19,066
